# Plan 9: Admin Panel - Blog Management

## Goal
Build the blog management interface with a WYSIWYG editor.

## Tasks
- [ ] Install **TipTap** (core, starter-kit, image extension).
- [ ] Create `app/admin/blog/page.tsx` (List) and `app/admin/blog/new/page.tsx` (Editor).
- [ ] Implement the Editor:
    - [ ] Use **TipTap** for the rich text area.
    - [ ] Use **ShadCN Button** for toolbar items (Bold, Italic, etc.).
    - [ ] Use **ShadCN Input** for the post title.
- [ ] Add image upload functionality within the editor.
- [ ] Create Server Actions to save/update posts.
- [ ] Add fields for SEO metadata and tags.
